                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h3>Commitment to Safety</h3>
                    <p>Your safety is our priority. We provide mods only after 14+ days of testing. Every file is scanned by over 100 antivirus engines via the VirusTotal API. If a harmful mod is detected, it is removed instantly, and the community is notified immediately.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Community Feature -->
            <div class="feature-item">
                <lottie-player src="/animations/heart.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; flex-shrink: 0;" loop autoplay></lottie-player>
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h3>The Power of Community</h3>
                    <p>GPL Mods doesn't just create mods; we are a community hub. Mods are uploaded by members and trusted sources, strictly distributed under the GNU/GPL spirit. We are a platform run by the people, for the people, ensuring 100% working content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- NEW: Open-Source Feature -->
            <div class="feature-item">
                <!-- IMPORTANT: Download a "code" or "open source" lottie file and save it as code.json in your animations folder! -->
                <lottie-player src="/animations/code.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; flex-shrink: 0;" loop autoplay></lottie-player>
                <div class="feature-text">
                    <h3>Open-Source Philosophy</h3>
                    <p>We believe in absolute transparency. GPL Mods embraces the open-source philosophy to its core. Our platform's infrastructure and the mods we distribute thrive on community collaboration, allowing developers to audit, contribute, and improve the ecosystem securely.</p>
